explanation: "The marked embryonic structure is the **notochord**, which persists in the adult as the **nucleus pulposus**.\nThe **annulus fibrosus** is derived from surrounding **mesenchyme (sclerotome)**, while vertebrae form from sclerotome and the spinal cord from neural tube.",
