explanation: "Marked structure A is the allantois, which forms the urachus, which in turn gives rise to the median umbilical ligament.<br><br><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/74b9f691-5c4d-462a-983a-74c1cc2d524b.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\"><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/6113ff35-7060-4a76-aa90-47531dfa748e.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
