subcategory: "10-pyqs",
tags: ["PYQ", "NEET PG 2022"],
text: "The structure marked A in the image below gives rise to which of the following structures?",
options: [{"id": "A", "text": "Gastrosplenic ligament", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "B", "text": "Lienorenal ligament", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "C", "text": "Falciform ligament", "is_correct": true}, {"id": "D", "text": "Gastrophrenic ligament", "is_correct": false}],
explanation: "The marked structure is the **ventral mesogastrium**, which gives rise to the **falciform ligament** and **lesser omentum**.<br><br>In contrast, the **gastrosplenic, lienorenal, and gastrophrenic ligaments** are derivatives of the **dorsal mesogastrium**.<br><br><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/b47cedd0-bdde-4d6e-ba2a-3d8fd8d7a30f.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
