explanation: "The marked cluster of cells represents the **Islets of Langerhans** within pancreatic tissue. The histological image shows the characteristic appearance of pancreatic parenchyma with dark eosinophilic areas representing serous acinar cells (exocrine pancreas) and lighter, less eosinophilic areas representing the islets of Langerhans (endocrine pancreas).<br><br><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/aba97f65-08f5-4bbb-b197-05dea1131fc9.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">",
images: [{"url": "https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/questions_image/01KKDT8HBWNPGSYBGPWWZNEF83.jpg", "caption": ""}]
